values:
First im gonna start with...guys look REALLY good in ~PINK~ shirts...right? ;)

Anyways, yesterday was a long day, but it really was a lot of fun. So Prateesh decided that we needed to be at his house at 10, got there at like 10:30, no one was there, and he hadn't even showered. yea, so was sleeping in his bed then Manisha decides to wake me up when she got there*like an hour later! with Richa and Niket* by hitting my ass as hard as possible. Well we sat in his room and made it smell like nail polish till Sunny and Karan got there. The funniest thing was when Prat decided to stand up on the fireplace and broke the ledge off. As bad as i felt it was really funny. And he tries to blame it on me cuz i was on it first, at least i wasn't standing on the ledge! Beant stopped by for a lil bit too, to get his part. Things just kept getting added to Richa's "needed" list. Sunny and Karan got hair cuts and looked sooo kyoote. I was deff laughing at like every little thing tho...not quite sure why. i went home a lil later and did the whole getting ready thing.

Then it was time for the PARTY. it started out with the usual snacks. Some people did dances. Beant and Deep had a kickass bhangra dance. Me and Richa danced too. There was a slide show that his brother, Sanjay, made that so was sooo cute! He definitely did "buck" on him in it.*spending so much time with these boys really does get you talking like them* Then our skits, which i think came out well too. It was funny :) Then of course, open dance...'nuff said. :) That was the best! im surprised my legs aren't in pain today. especially since we did *dhol baje* twice. *Chris i'll be sure to teach you that step before the next big party :P* 

Today is gonna be the first day in like a week that i don't see any of these *ugly* kids. Just spending the day with my dad, and out to dinner later. But we already have plans for tuesday night...PARTYYYYY!! woohooo. haha

Well one week of summer is ALREADY gone...gotta make the best of the rest...:)

leave love...make me laugh

Where do i even begin? the past couple of days have been a lot of fun.Tuesday me, karan, manisha, and sunny all went to Richa's. Niket and Prateesh were there for a lil bit. we had some AWESOME mango shakes...and some laughs over grrrreat stuff *i love Mridul Aunty:)* Wednesday... Richa, Sunny, Karan, Niket, and I went to Prateesh's. We got caught in the rain while walking to Ruby Tuesday's for lunch, and deffinately had some intresting things happen there. Prateesh only went through 3 bottles of ketchup too! we dried off on the way home, since the sun decided to finally come out. Most of Aneesh's grad skit came along afterwards. Prateesh left for Beach week, and the rest of us went to Richa's and just hung out. Karan and Niket were "watching" The Last Samuri...ALONE. who knows what they were doing. haha just kidding. We had some interesting conversations on the phone with some drunk kids...only if i could have taped him :) The boys left around 11 and i stayed the night. Everyone came over to my house thursday...and yesterday we went Manisha's except Karan and Sunny cuz they had something at VCU. Aimee took us to get slurpees!!! wooohooooo. i love that girl. Later was Niket's surprise 16th brithday party. HE HAD NOOOOOO CLUE! his reaction was great! he looked sooo kyoote all dressed up...hehe. so his party was like a pre-party for tonight:) i'll be sure to let you all know what goes down. i only got like 6 hours of sleep and right now im heading to Prateesh's so we can get these skits down. They are gonna be FUNNY! Can't wait for tonight... more later, lEaVe LoVe

interesting day. in a good mood :) had some fun, thought about some stuff. DIFFERENT things happened today. our phone is finaly fixed...its so nice to hear it ring again. im in a singing stage...which can be kinda terrifying for others...but hey, not my problem.

Much love to Tatiana for beautifying this site...and Sarah for giving me the site for the picture. As of now im waiting for the guys to come fix my phone...more later

Sunny...FALL BACK!

Today was a good day :) i slept in late...and just hung around the house. haven't done that in a while. Then later was Ryan's going away party. he sure was surprised...but i loved his way of just poppin peanuts in his mouth! It was chill and i had a good time. I really am gonna miss you Ryan! There were crazy water fights goin on, and sierra mist from my part too...hehehe. I accidentally dropped Aaron and hurt him...i can't help it his legs were slippery! i feel SOOO bad.

The Lakers lost once again today...WOOHOO!! Pistons are gonna show them what's up tues. when they slaughter and send 'em home. Oh how much i hate the Lakers!

Manisha comes home from Maryland tomorrow, and Aimee from India. Our phone is supposed to finally be fixed tomorrow after 10 day. This week should be exciting...looking forward to it, as well as the rest of the next three months...

LeAvE sOmE lOvIn

Its the first day of summer vacation...and it MOST DEFINITELY hasn't hit me yet. i didn't get to sleep in today, because i went to York's graduation. i don't think i've ever laughed so much that early in the morning as i did on the way up to William and Mary. "Prateesh you are ugly, stupid, and an idiot. that is a bad combination. why are you so green maaaan?" Anyways, i wasn't even graduating and i was nerve wreck cuz Aneeshdidn't get there till 5 minutes before his name was called! The things his parents did for him to make sure he got to his graduation since his flight got canceled! :) At least he still got to make his valedictorian speech, and it was good mr. harvard. After wards we went back to Richa's house and just chylled. Then i went shopping with my parents for a lil bit *oh how much i love me some shopping!* came home, had dinner then Richa came over to my house. she just left, and im extremely tired and going to bed now. Goodnight my loves *Congrats Graduates*
